    - Using < instead of &lt;    (rarely needed)
    - Forgetting to close tags   (<value>text</value>)
  Validate your file at: https://www.xmlvalidation.com

  TRANSLATION EXAMPLE
  Before (English source):
    <data name="RefreshButton" xml:space="preserve"><value>Refresh</value></data>

  After (Spanish translation):
    <data name="RefreshButton" xml:space="preserve"><value>Actualizar</value></data>

